Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:24.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}第6道菜\N宗太的憂鬱、小鳥遊家的女人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太明明以前那麼可愛的說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.63,0:02:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在要是還那樣子就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那種東西快給我丟掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢  這可是過世的爸爸拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這卷錄影帶就像是遺物般的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然完全沒把爸爸拍進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的錄影有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是長男  所以很疼他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…真希望能好好以長男的樣子來養育啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那樣繼續作為女孩子活下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞎說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:03:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  沒有戀愛小說的素材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又遇到瓶頸期了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我們家都是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梢動不動就換對象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薺還是小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一枝姐是離婚回娘家的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有資格說別人嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  雖說女人多  但我們家的這幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法作為戀愛小說的素材的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要是說到女人多的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.05,0:03:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天相馬休息  這是兩人份
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}3月14日  白色情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吃的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能送給店長真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我沒那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏子姐的份我已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  情人節那時候不也給她巧克力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長明明是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:04:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  她比男人還帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就收回禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  佐藤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杏子姐是女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用日語無法交流…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐藤還是一樣慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}不方便進入休息室…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是回禮  請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特意回禮  真是不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像反而勞您費心了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  你的口氣好像大嬸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家才不是大嬸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起  你還是小朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家才不是小朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  不要耍我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？回禮？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  謝謝伊波小姐了  請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉啊  讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好遠  完全沒有要給我的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不想被你揍嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫…莫非你想丟過來給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那麼做的話就太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}3980日元（含稅）\N（股份制）映一玩具製造  訂購電話  1231233526789－1235746813\N巧奪天工  魔術手  （限定100台）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是郵購的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  親手交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說…「謝謝你特意為了我買這個」嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮夾  有這麼多？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  聽說你每天都在換
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請拿去做補充吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這種的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種的…應該抱著感謝的心情去使用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該好好保存起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我太慌張了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西…自出生以來第一次收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那個…請不要太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那我折中一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時好好保存一段時間再使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她高興成那樣…弄得我都有點不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}新道具  魔術手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又醉得不省人事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢姐  不要在玄關睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  宗太隨便進人家的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來偷情的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我睡一輩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太～姐姐又被甩了啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  也沒人把你拖進房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝了酒也不想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.71,0:06:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我是想幫忙處理一下小梢的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.42,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果去搬比筆重的東西的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會肌肉痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是三天後才發作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:19.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太  姐姐好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我對泉姐沒有抱過任何期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  安慰姐姐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  快截稿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回房間寫稿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太  不要太寵泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一枝姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  泉也給我好好站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…站起來很累的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宗  幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在截稿前  我的身體比平時都要虛弱的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.71,0:07:48.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太  給我酒～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我酒～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想和她吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一枝姐瞪了一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在看你而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  眼神好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你不站起來  被俯視感覺好像被瞪了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身高也不矮的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你打算當小說家到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年到頭整天說工作工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去  做得也不是很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一直穿著黑衣  連我的心情也跟著變鬱悶了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著就…這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊啊  真讓人火大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太也是  自己的房間讓她自己收拾去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她說了她很虛弱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.33,0:08:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小說也沒什麼進展  沒打掃的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.61,0:08:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱到連自己的事都無法做好  還沒有進展的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:08:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明這工作不適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不算遲  放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…說錯什麼話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一枝姐你不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你們根本就合不來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  歡迎回家  真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.97,0:09:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白色情人節的回禮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  收到了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  這不是很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要怎麼辦才好呢  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴上不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  突然就戴上去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會讓人覺得太輕飄飄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒這回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟了也很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是但是…難得收到這麼可愛的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去好開心呢  真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該出來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我進去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我自己的事自己做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想收拾一下房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而弄得更髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉…你現在幾歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剛才的話忘記吧  是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一枝姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:11:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之那啥  不要太鑽牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得要轉換心情  注意休息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看電視  出去走走  聽聽別人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定就能從完全無關的地方找到小說素材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有夢想沒有希望的一枝姐直到離婚的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能成為戀愛小說的素材呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  小鳥遊沒有什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢啊  要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  雖然很穩重  但也還是個高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該有很多想要的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠打工的錢還不夠用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月真的很緊張呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家計
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家計？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.34,0:12:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  怎麼減都不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用品也完全用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個月還剩5天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  都是因為無計劃地亂用才會導致不足的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要省著點用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不都是因為你把生活費用來亂喝酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家這個月不停地被甩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工資也都用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算去拜託一枝姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她每個月也只會給定額的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉姐因為快截稿了  整天把自己關在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了  自掏腰包去取些存款吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.35,0:12:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是錢的話  這裡有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.72,0:12:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼弄到的…這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對一枝姐說了以後  她馬上就給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後生可畏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  薺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了  關於梢姐的酒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼酒  只要有酒她就會很高興地喝掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多買些便宜貨放著比較划算哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薺已經小學六年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了哥哥一直在急速成長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  個頭高得讓人有哭的衝動  薺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  更依賴我一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薺  你為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐們也變得能隨心所欲地操控了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹會因為我  成長為很可怕的惡女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是不去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太  你要去哪裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜託你  買點酒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己買去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想再喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不喝就會活不下去的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等飯後也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫我打掃房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  你老是對泉姐那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  宗太是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  今天又醉上一層樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宗  請你原諒小梢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是很怕寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  請和對待我一樣  平等地照顧小梢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說照顧…我可不是當媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  宗太拽什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我就讓他討厭到底好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把宗太喜歡的小小可愛物全部虐得稀巴爛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？還以為他房間會放滿可愛東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是個很普通的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…是我以前送他的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間裡只有這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只把這個擺在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非宗太他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.56,0:15:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…很喜歡我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢姐  最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梢姐也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能治治她整天醉到晚的毛病就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝  我有事麻煩你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要吃咖哩飯  但沒有飯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都說了這個時間人太多了不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行  我會見一個男人打飛一個的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐  你在這地方做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊波小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是的  我只是想去一下超市…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你冷靜一下  再這麼下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會發生慘劇的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  在去人來人往的地方前發現你真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  還讓你幫我去買
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣  順便而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才發覺  你這樣子在上學路上居然沒出過事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  早上一大早出門的話  就不會碰到人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到打工的餐廳  我認識條很偏僻的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的時候都選擇沒有人的暗路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是間諜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不用啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放心丟下你一個人回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打了路人  也很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反…反正我也只是在離你很遠的身後跟著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要牽手？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  還好有帶著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到她還真的抓著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一枝姐  你現在回家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工那邊的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.46,0:17:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去超市的時候  剛好碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正送她回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這想法雖然很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？剛才不是說明過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的打工地方  流行著這種奇怪的感情陪養方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚…晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伊波真晝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你真有禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  我是宗太的姐姐一枝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟平時都受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊的姐姐  好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前見過的姐姐也很大…好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是…襲擊他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  對不起  說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說平時都受他的照顧的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…實際上襲擊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我是有在襲擊他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊波小姐你可以暫時閉嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太  你過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.35,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊什麼的到底是什麼樣的交往方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實是有被她襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是她的癖好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.90,0:19:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是為了讓你搞不純異性交往  才允許你打工的  宗太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好像被誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是一見到男人就會揍過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男性恐懼症
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這種襲擊啊  那就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.69,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那樣的話  請盡情揍他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很結實的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得他在家也夠嗆…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小鳥遊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很近了  到這裡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.78,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話  請收下蘋果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很便宜就買了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  打工再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.28,0:20:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢  宗太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是姐姐搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你沒事吧  梢姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.65,0:20:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝多了嗎  還是生了怪病？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.92,0:20:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不舒服的話  去一下醫院比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一枝姐也一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  偶然碰到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家用三盒裝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  原稿用紙和墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢  泉姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡宗太哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的怪怪的啊  梢姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.43,0:20:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗太～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.82,0:20:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿用紙  謝謝你了  小宗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真晝 其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.57,0:21:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼 晚飯很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思い通りにゃすすまない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:32.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有點不能稱心如意地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.66,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋に大事なコミュニケート
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.66,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達戀愛中最重要的訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんなコトバが命中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣的言語才能打動她的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:41.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国語辞典をめくろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:41.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻翻國語辭典吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:56.92,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おもむろに問わず語りで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:56.92,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再曖昧不清
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い気持ちを告げましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢地把熾熱的心意告訴她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,されどインギンなこの胸は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心中的這份真情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ジョウゼツにはならない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:05.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法口若懸河的表達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:08.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物音にデリケートです
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:08.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點膽小敏感的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守る身の術しりません
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:11.10,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會防身術
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:14.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど担当は矢面です
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:14.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作護花使者是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:17.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常に現場勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:17.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不臨陣脫逃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心意気を高らかに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.02,0:22:20.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中滿懷著激情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:25.38,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自弁モードにTRYしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.91,0:22:25.38,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按自己的風格行動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハートのエッジに挑もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起挑戰心靈的極限吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:32.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思うだけ見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.68,0:22:32.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想盡情與你對視
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もしかしたらとアトランダム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許時機難以預測
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:38.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,チャンスを待ってみるべき
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:38.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也會耐心等待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ハートのエースを捲ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:41.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出自己心中的王牌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,念力で見つめて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:44.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾注心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:47.86,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛の形のシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.99,0:22:47.86,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼剪出愛的形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,イメージを探りだそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:50.97,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照心中的理想形象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:53.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙い通りにすすみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:53.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若想達成預期目標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.67,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ネコの背中をまねしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:57.67,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得蓄勢待發隨時準備出擊

Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  梢姐怎麼把門搞壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.26,0:23:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的房間裡沒擺多少可愛東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  自從小時候\N我很喜歡帶來帶去的兔子玩偶被弄得破爛不堪以後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個以外的玩偶  為了不弄髒  都好好收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.27,0:23:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.51,0:23:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  這本字典可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這孩子好好擺起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集預告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.70,0:23:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.86,0:23:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  羞鳥遊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音尾先生回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.81,0:23:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還有  這次帶回的禮物是個女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好久不見的音尾和新打工員=山田(!?)」
